# Pearl store runtime files — keep the dolt manifest + content-
# addressed blobs in git (so pearls sync between machines via git
# push/pull), but exclude anything ephemeral.

# Per-process lock files
*/.dolt/noms/LOCK

# Temp / scratch dirs
*/.dolt/temptf/
*/.dolt/noms/.temptf/

# Stats engine sidecar (rebuilt on demand)
*/.dolt/stats/
